name: Bespoke
description:
Custom designed, one of a kind evening wear, made to measure for individual clientele. I will help you realize your dream look. Nothing is impossible.

You will sit down with me and design, take measurements and select fabrics. The price is a starting price, price quotes come after the first meeting, which is complementary. You will be prompted to purchase the option with your name when it is time to buy, after our first design consultation, when we confirm fabrics, design, and future fitting appointments.

name: Accessories
description:
NJPaganelli accessories feature patchwork and upcycling. I use my fabric scraps or your unused and/or ill fitting clothes to create bags or neckwear.
